# Fully Responsive Native App-Like Navigation System

Transform the navigation experience into a highly responsive, modern, app-like interface for mobile devices, tablets, and desktop displays.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Key UX Enhancements Introduced:**
> - **Mobile Bottom Application Dock**: A fixed native-app style bottom navigation bar for mobile screens featuring instant access to **Dashboard**, **Campaigns**, **Quick Add (+)**, **Leads**, and **Menu**.
> - **Mobile Quick Search Drawer**: Dedicated mobile search trigger and slide-down modal for searching leads, campaigns, users, and reports on mobile.
> - **Mobile Bottom Sheets**: Quick Actions, Notifications, Theme Selector, and Profile menus dynamically transition into touch-friendly bottom sheets on small screens instead of overflowing popovers.
> - **Drawer & Layout Polishing**: Close button on mobile sidebar, improved backdrop blur, and content padding adjustments to prevent clipping.

